        "heading": "Waste Per Person Dropped Sharply from 2000",
        "body": "In the chart below, you'll see the amount of waste per person peaked at 273 kg in 2000. After that, there was a steady decline, dropping 37% to 173 kg by 2012. This suggests that residents have become more conscientious about waste, making efforts to reduce their output.",
